posts.text:
Yapay Zekayı Profesyonel Kullanın!
Herkes yapay zekayı kullanıyor ama verim alamıyor. GEMINI, CHATGPT ve GROK için modele özel en etkili promptlar.
Kaydedin, maksimum verim alın!
1\. Öğrenmek istediğiniz uzun videoları veya uzun yazıları, özetle diyerek vakit kaybetmeyin. Bunları yapıştırın:
Gemini:
{
"protocol\_type": "Deep\_Learning\_Analysis",
"target\_model": "Gemini\_Ultra\_Pro",
"context\_configuration": {
"role": "Academic Research Assistant",
"analysis\_depth": "High-Definition",
"output\_language": "Turkish"
},
"processing\_directives": {
"step\_1": "Extract core thesis and underlying logic.",
"step\_2": "Identify 5 critical data points or arguments.",
"step\_3": "Synthesize a 'Mental Map' of the content.",
"step\_4": "Generate 3 'What-If' scenarios to test understanding."
},
"data\_structure\_required": {
"summary": "string",
"key\_nodes": "array",
"technical\_glossary": "map",
"actionable\_insights": "list"
}
}
ChatGPT:
{
"system\_prompt": {
"persona": "Expert Consultant & Educator",
"objective": "Summarize long-form content into a 5-minute mastery guide.",
"style\_guide": "Professional, concise, and bold headings."
},
"input\_processing": {
"source\_material": "\[İÇERİĞİ BURAYA YAPIŞTIRIN VEYA ÖZETLEYİN\]",
"constraints": \[\
"No corporate jargon",\
"Explain complex terms with analogies",\
"Highlight contradictory points"\
\]
},
"output\_workflow": \[\
"Executive Summary (Max 200 words)",\
"Top 5 Practical Applications",\
"The 'One Sentence' Takeaway",\
"Curated Q&A for Quick Review"\
\]
}
Grok:
{
"grok\_config": {
"mode": "Analytic\_Rigorous",
"filter\_noise": true,
"prioritize\_logic": true
},
"logic\_gate": {
"if\_content\_is\_video": "Focus on narrative arc and key timestamps.",
"if\_content\_is\_report": "Focus on methodology, data results, and conclusion."
},
"extraction\_rules": {
"primary\_argument": "REQUIRED",
"evidence\_quality": "EVALUATE",
"conclusion\_validity": "CHECK"
},
"final\_report\_format": "Technical Markdown"
}
👉 2\. Sıradan bir CV ile günümüz iş dünyasında fark yaratmak imkansız. Yapay zekaya sadece "CV’mi düzenle" derseniz, size vasat bir sonuç verir.
Gemini:
{
"operation": "CV\_Semantic\_Alignment",
"target\_engine": "Gemini\_Multimodal",
"data\_inputs": {
"current\_cv": "\[CV\_METNİNİZİ\_BURAYA\_EKLEYİN\]",
"target\_job\_description": "\[HEDEF\_İŞ\_TANIMINI\_BURAYA\_EKLEYİN\]"
},
"optimization\_logic": {
"keyword\_extraction": "Identify high-priority industry keywords.",
"gap\_analysis": "Highlight missing skills based on the job description.",
"rephrasing\_engine": "Convert passive tasks into impact-driven achievements."
},
"output\_schema": {
"professional\_summary": "Impactful 3-line hook",
"mapped\_skills": "List of top 10 relevant competencies",
"experience\_refactor": "Bullet points using Google's XYZ formula"
}
}
ChatGPT:
{
"system\_instruction": {
"persona": "Senior Technical Recruiter",
"methodology": "STAR\_Formula (Situation, Task, Action, Result)",
"tone": "Professional & Quantifiable"
},
"processing\_steps": \[\
"Analyze the input CV for metrics and numbers.",\
"Cross-reference with industry standards for the specific role.",\
"Rewrite each bullet point to start with a strong action verb."\
\],
"constraints": {
"ats\_compliance": true,
"no\_fluff\_words": true,
"quantify\_results": "Mandatory (e.g., %, $, Time)"
},
"execution": "Rewrite the CV in professional Markdown format."
}
Grok:
{
"grok\_analyzer": {
"mode": "Competitive\_Edge\_Detection",
"focus": "Marketability & Leadership"
},
"logic\_gates": {
"if\_vague\_description": "Replace with data-backed achievement.",
"if\_irrelevant\_info": "Deprioritize or remove to save space.",
"if\_leadership\_potential": "Elevate to the top of the section."
},
"report\_structure": {
"critique": "What is wrong with the current CV?",
"optimized\_version": "The new, high-impact CV",
"interview\_prep\_notes": "3 potential questions based on the new CV"
}
}
👉 3\. Viral İçerik Üretim Protokolü Algoritma Avcısı
Gemini:
{
"protocol": "Viral\_Vector\_Analysis",
"engine": "Gemini\_Multimodal\_Pro",
"input\_data": {
"topic": "\[KONUYU\_BURAYA\_YAZIN\]",
"target\_platform": "X (Twitter)",
"audience\_segment": "Tech & Productivity Enthusiasts"
},
"algorithmic\_directives": {
"hook\_engineering": "Create 5 psychological hooks (Fear of Missing Out, Curiosity Gap, Contrarian Truth).",
"retention\_logic": "Structure the thread to increase 'dwell time' (okuma süresi).",
"virality\_metrics": \["Shareability", "Save-worthiness", "Controversy\_Level"\]
},
"output\_structure": {
"hook\_options": "List",
"content\_body": "Thread\_Format",
"visual\_suggestions": "DALL-E/Midjourney\_Prompts"
}
}
ChatGPT:
{
"system\_config": {
"role": "Growth Hacker & Content Strategist",
"strategy": "High-Value\_Edu-Tainment",
"goal": "Maximize Retweets and Bookmarks"
},
"content\_refactoring": {
"original\_idea": "\[FİKRİNİZİ\_BURAYA\_YAZIN\]",
"formatting\_rules": \[\
"Use white space effectively for readability.",\
"Bullet points for quick scanning.",\
"End with a high-friction Call to Action (CTA)."\
\]
},
"psychological\_layers": {
"authority": "Use data or case studies.",
"scarcity": "Highlight why this information is rare.",
"community": "Ask a question that sparks debate."
},
"output\_format": "Markdown\_Optimized\_For\_X"
}
Grok:
{
"grok\_protocol": {
"mode": "Unfiltered\_Analytical",
"real\_time\_sync": true
},
"logic\_flow": {
"step\_1": "Analyze current trending sentiment on the topic.",
"step\_2": "Identify a 'popular but wrong' opinion to challenge (Contrarian Hook).",
"step\_3": "Craft a sharp, punchy response that forces people to stop scrolling."
},
"technical\_constraints": {
"max\_characters\_per\_post": 280,
"tone": "Witty, Bold, and Sharp",
"use\_memes": "Strategic\_Suggestions"
}
}
👉 4\. Finansal Otorite Odaklı: Karmaşık piyasa verilerini veya yatırım kararlarını nasıl analiz ediyorsunuz? Sadece "bu mantıklı mı?" diye sormak yeterli değil.
Gemini:
{
"protocol": "Financial\_Macro\_Synthesis",
"engine": "Gemini\_Pro\_Finance",
"input\_data": {
"asset\_name": "\[VARLIK\_ADI\_Veya\_VERİ\_SETİ\]",
"timeframe": "Mid-to-Long Term",
"risk\_profile": "Conservative/Aggressive"
},
"analytical\_layers": {
"fundamental\_check": \["Revenue Growth", "EBITDA Margin", "Debt/Equity Ratio"\],
"macro\_environment": \["Interest Rate Impact", "Inflation Sensitivity"\],
"correlation\_analysis": "Compare with benchmark indices (S&P 500, BIST100, etc.)"
},
"output\_schema": {
"executive\_summary": "High-level verdict",
"strength\_weakness\_matrix": "Table",
"probability\_scenarios": \["Best Case", "Base Case", "Worst Case"\]
}
}
ChatGPT:
{
"system\_config": {
"role": "Chartered Financial Analyst (CFA)",
"framework": "Value\_Investing\_Principles",
"precision\_level": "High"
},
"analysis\_workflow": {
"step\_1": "Analyze the balance sheet and cash flow statements.",
"step\_2": "Evaluate competitive advantages (Moat Analysis).",
"step\_3": "Check technical indicators (RSI, Moving Averages, Support/Resistance).",
"step\_4": "Perform a DCF (Discounted Cash Flow) estimation."
},
"constraints": {
"ignore\_hype": true,
"focus\_on\_metrics": "Mandatory",
"identify\_red\_flags": true
},
"output\_format": "Professional Analyst Report"
}
Grok:
{
"grok\_engine": {
"mode": "Market\_Sentiment\_Monitor",
"real\_time\_analysis": true
},
"logic\_gates": {
"sentiment\_check": "Is the crowd overly bullish or bearish?",
"insider\_activity": "Are there any notable institutional movements?",
"hype\_vs\_reality": "Contrast social media buzz with actual financial data."
},
"risk\_assessment": {
"liquidity\_risk": "Evaluate trading volume.",
"volatility\_index": "Measure current price fluctuations.",
"contrarian\_view": "Provide a reason NOT to invest in this asset."
}
}
👉 5\. Profesyonel İletişim ve Zor E-postalar:
İnsanlar iş hayatında hayır demekte, zam istemekte veya bir hatayı kabul etmekte zorlanıyor. Agresif veya çok yumuşak bir taslağı "iddialı ama nazik" bir profesyonel metne dönüştürme.
Gemini:
{
"protocol": "Strategic\_Communication\_Design",
"engine": "Gemini\_Pro\_Nuance",
"input\_context": {
"scenario": "\[ZOR\_DURUM\_AÇIKLAMASI\]",
"recipient\_role": "\[ALICI\_POZİSYONU\]",
"desired\_outcome": "Resolution without friction"
},
"communication\_parameters": {
"tone": "Diplomatic, Empathetic, but Professional",
"power\_dynamic\_balancing": "High",
"structure": "Sandwich Method (Positive - Critical - Positive)"
},
"output\_requirement": {
"email\_draft": "Turkish",
"strategy\_notes": "Explain why these specific words were chosen."
}
}
ChatGPT:
{
"system\_instruction": {
"persona": "Expert Executive Coach",
"methodology": "Value-Based Negotiation",
"focus": "Win-Win Framework"
},
"message\_architecture": {
"core\_argument": "\[BAŞARILARINIZ\_VEYA\_GEREKÇENİZ\]",
"addressing\_objections": "Pre-emptively solve potential 'No' answers.",
"call\_to\_action": "Clear and low-pressure meeting request."
},
"technical\_constraints": {
"brevity": "Under 150 words",
"avoid\_weak\_words": \["I think", "maybe", "sorry for bothering"\],
"emphasize\_metrics": true
},
"execution": "Generate 3 variations (Direct, Collaborative, Formal)."
}
Grok:
{
"grok\_config": {
"mode": "Efficient\_Corporate\_Direct",
"no\_fluff": true
},
"logic\_gate": {
"if\_saying\_no": "Offer a brief alternative or a later date.",
"if\_admitting\_mistake": "Own the error immediately and present the fix.",
"if\_setting\_boundary": "Be firm but helpful."
},
"output\_style": {
"clarity\_score": "10/10",
"emotional\_intelligence": "Balanced",
"vibe": "High-Status Professional"
}
}
👉 6\. Veri ve Excel Sihirbazı: Çoğu beyaz yakalı veya öğrenci Excel formülleriyle boğuşuyor. Yapay zekaya sadece "Şu hücreyi şuna topla" derseniz, büyük veri setlerinde hata yapma olasılığı artar.
Gemini:
{
"protocol": "Excel\_Schema\_Architecture",
"engine": "Gemini\_Data\_Expert",
"input\_context": {
"data\_description": "\[TABLONUZUN\_İÇERİĞİNİ\_AÇIKLAYIN\]",
"goal": "Create a robust formula for \[HEDEF\_İŞLEM\]",
"source\_columns": \["Sütun A: İsim", "Sütun B: Tarih", "Sütun C: Tutar"\]
},
"logic\_requirements": {
"error\_handling": "Include IFERROR logic.",
"scalability": "Ensure the formula works for 10,000+ rows.",
"dynamic\_ranges": "Use INDEX/MATCH or XLOOKUP instead of VLOOKUP."
},
"output\_schema": {
"formula\_code": "The exact Excel syntax",
"logic\_explanation": "Step-by-step breakdown of how the formula works",
"data\_cleaning\_tips": "How to prepare the data before applying."
}
}
ChatGPT:
{
"system\_instruction": {
"role": "Expert Data Analyst & VBA Developer",
"task": "Automate a repetitive Excel workflow.",
"precision\_level": "Absolute"
},
"workflow\_steps": \[\
"1\. Analyze the raw data format provided.",\
"2\. Propose the most efficient method (Power Query vs VBA vs Formula).",\
"3\. Provide the complete code or formula block.",\
"4\. Add comments to the code for easy customization."\
\],
"constraints": {
"no\_manual\_steps": true,
"handle\_blank\_cells": "Ignore or fill with zero",
"localization": "Use \[ENGLISH/TURKISH\] formula syntax."
},
"output\_format": "Clean Markdown with Copy-Paste Code Blocks"
}
Grok:
{
"grok\_engine": {
"mode": "Data\_Optimization\_Streamlined",
"focus": "Efficiency and Performance"
},
"logic\_gate": {
"if\_file\_size\_large": "Avoid volatile functions like OFFSET or INDIRECT.",
"if\_data\_messy": "Provide a REGEX or Power Query solution.",
"if\_summary\_needed": "Suggest Pivot Table structure instead of complex formulas."
},
"report\_output": {
"optimized\_formula": "REQUIRED",
"performance\_note": "Why this version is faster.",
"quick\_fix\_checklist": "3 things to check if the formula fails."
}
}
👉 7\. Kimse 50 sayfalık kullanım koşullarını veya iş sözleşmelerini okumuyor. Metni analiz edip aleyhte olan maddeleri veya gizli ücretleri bulma.
Gemini:
{
"protocol": "Legal\_Anomaly\_Detection",
"engine": "Gemini\_Pro\_1.5\_Flash",
"document\_analysis": {
"target\_text": "\[SÖZLEŞME\_VEYA\_METİN\_BURAYA\]",
"audit\_depth": "High\_Detail",
"risk\_tolerance": "Zero"
},
"scanning\_vectors": {
"hidden\_costs": \["Maintenance fees", "Service charges", "Automatic renewals"\],
"legal\_traps": \["Arbitration clauses", "Limitation of liability", "Data sharing"\],
"user\_disadvantage": \["Termination penalties", "Non-compete clauses"\]
},
"output\_schema": {
"executive\_summary": "Top 3 most dangerous points",
"risk\_matrix": "Categorized table of risks",
"action\_plan": "Specific questions to ask the other party"
}
}
ChatGPT:
{
"system\_instruction": {
"role": "Corporate Legal Consultant",
"framework": "Consumer\_Protection\_Standard",
"objective": "Identify every clause where the user gives up a right or gains a liability."
},
"audit\_workflow": \[\
"1\. Scan for all currency ($/TL) signs and numbers to find hidden fees.",\
"2\. Identify 'Automatic' or 'Renew' keywords for subscription traps.",\
"3\. Highlight 'Governing Law' and 'Jurisdiction' sections.",\
"4\. Translate complex legalese into simple Turkish warnings."\
\],
"constraints": {
"plain\_language": true,
"highlight\_red\_flags": "Mandatory",
"no\_summary": "Focus only on problematic parts"
},
"formatting": "Markdown with Bold Warnings"
}
Grok:
{
"grok\_audit": {
"mode": "Skeptical\_Analyst",
"focus": "Catching\_The\_Fine\_Print"
},
"logic\_gate": {
"if\_vague\_language": "Flag as potential trap.",
"if\_one\_sided\_termination": "Highlight as critical risk.",
"if\_data\_harvesting": "Detail what data is being taken."
},
"final\_report": {
"the\_catch": "Where is the hidden trap?",
"money\_leaks": "Direct or indirect costs.",
"verdict": "Sign or Decline?"
}
}
👉 8\. Pazarlama ve İkna Psikolojisi: Bir ürünü veya kendini pazarlamak isteyen herkesin ortak sancısı. Sıradan bir açıklamayı; pazarlama çerçevelerine sokarak yeniden yazma.
Gemini:
{
"protocol": "Persuasion\_Architecture\_Mapping",
"engine": "Gemini\_Pro\_Marketing",
"input\_data": {
"product\_name": "\[ÜRÜN\_VEYA\_KENDİNİZ\]",
"raw\_description": "\[SIRADAN\_AÇIKLAMA\_BURAYA\]",
"target\_audience": "\[HEDEF\_KİTLE\_PROFİLİ\]"
},
"framework\_selection": {
"primary": "StoryBrand (7-Step Hero's Journey)",
"secondary": "The 4 C's (Clear, Concise, Compelling, Credible)"
},
"psychological\_triggers": \["Authority", "Social Proof", "Liking"\],
"output\_schema": {
"brand\_script": "Narrative structure where the customer is the hero.",
"value\_proposition": "One sentence that defines why you are the best.",
"emotional\_hooks": "3 psychological hooks for different buyer personas."
}
}
ChatGPT:
{
"system\_instruction": {
"role": "Senior Direct Response Copywriter",
"strategy": "Conversion-Rate-Optimization (CRO)",
"tone": "Persuasive and Solution-Oriented"
},
"copywriting\_workflow": \[\
"1\. Analyze the input for the 'Main Pain Point'.",\
"2\. Apply PAS (Problem, Agitation, Solution) framework.",\
"3\. Apply AIDA (Attention, Interest, Desire, Action) framework.",\
"4\. Cross-check for FOMO (Fear of Missing Out) elements."\
\],
"constraints": {
"active\_voice\_only": true,
"no\_corporate\_fluff": true,
"strong\_cta\_required": "Mandatory"
},
"execution": "Generate two variations: one short-form (social media) and one long-form (email/landing page)."
}
Grok:
{
"grok\_protocol": {
"mode": "High\_Stakes\_Sales",
"focus": "Attention\_Grabbing\_Contrarianism"
},
"logic\_gates": {
"if\_boring\_intro": "Replace with a shock-statement or a question.",
"if\_generic\_promise": "Make it ultra-specific with numbers/data.",
"if\_low\_urgency": "Add a scarcity factor or a time-bound risk."
},
"output\_style": {
"headlines": "5 'Scroll-Stopper' Options",
"body\_copy": "Direct and punchy with no-nonsense language.",
"risk\_reversal": "A guarantee that eliminates buyer remorse."
}
}
👉 9\. Kişisel Zaman Yönetimi ve Kaos Düzenleyici: Günü çok yoğun olan ama nereden başlayacağını bilmeyenler için.
Gemini:
{
"protocol": "Hierarchical\_Time\_Blocking",
"engine": "Gemini\_Pro\_Productivity",
"input\_chaos": {
"task\_list": "\[GÖREVLERİNİZİ\_RÖSTGELE\_BURAYA\_YAZIN\]",
"total\_available\_hours": "\[KAÇ\_SAATİNİZ\_VAR\]",
"energy\_profile": "High in morning, low after lunch"
},
"logic\_layers": {
"deep\_work\_identification": "Identify tasks requiring 90+ mins of focus.",
"batch\_processing": "Group similar small tasks (emails, calls) together.",
"buffer\_allocation": "Add 15% slack time for unexpected interruptions."
},
"output\_schema": {
"visual\_schedule": "Hour-by-hour table",
"priority\_nodes": "Top 3 non-negotiable tasks",
"energy\_alignment\_score": "Evaluate how well the plan fits your energy."
}
}
ChatGPT:
{
"system\_instruction": {
"role": "High-Performance Productivity Coach",
"methodology": \["Eisenhower Matrix", "Pareto Principle", "Time Boxing"\],
"objective": "Transform a messy list into a strategic strike plan."
},
"processing\_workflow": \[\
"1\. Categorize tasks into: Urgent/Important, Not Urgent/Important, etc.",\
"2\. Identify the 20% of tasks that will yield 80% of the results.",\
"3\. Apply 'Eat the Frog' technique for the most difficult task first.",\
"4\. Suggest tasks to delegate or eliminate."\
\],
"constraints": {
"realistic\_estimates": true,
"include\_breaks": "Pomodoro (50/10) style",
"focus\_on\_impact": "High"
},
"execution\_format": "Numbered Action List with Estimated Durations"
}
Grok:
{
"grok\_optimizer": {
"mode": "Zero\_Friction\_Execution",
"focus": "Eliminating\_Decision\_Fatigue"
},
"logic\_gates": {
"if\_task\_takes\_under\_2\_mins": "Command: DO IT NOW.",
"if\_task\_is\_vague": "Action: Breakdown into 3 sub-steps.",
"if\_schedule\_is\_full": "Logic: Auto-reschedule lowest priority to tomorrow."
},
"final\_output": {
"immediate\_next\_step": "The single most important thing to do right now.",
"avoidance\_warning": "What are you likely to procrastinate on today?",
"efficiency\_hack": "One tip to speed up today's workflow."
}
}
Evet sona geldik buraya kadar okuduğun için teşekkürler. Yapay zekayı bir sohbet botu olarak değil, bir işletim sistemi gibi kullanmaya başladığınızda asıl verim başlar. Başka hangi konuda komutlar gelsin yorumlarda belirtin, hazırlayalım...
